  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Relief Support - Nepal Earthquake</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. Mobilize volunteers, Staff, and member to distribute relief packages of medicine, water purifiers, masks, and sanitary napkins to affected areas in Bungamati, Sankhu, Lubu, Khokana  
2.  Reach out to women who are birthing, nursing, post/prenatal and have been displaces due to the earthquake. 
3. Visit the makeshift camps in Kathmandu, Bhaktapur and Lalitpur and direct women in need of care to the correct places as well as distribute clothing and food. 
4. Visit the camps to assess the situation and do a campaign on health and hygiene awareness since there is a danger of an epidemic due to unhealthy living conditions, open defecation and disease.</narrative>
  </description>
